{"title":"鸦片战争一百五十年祭","authors":["沈仁康"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":6,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸦片战争一百五十年祭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈仁康"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这声音不会衰老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白草山上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看川鼻洋滔滔的一角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一层一层的涟漪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一张密纹唱片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兀自转动到了今朝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮的咆哮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"义兵的呼号，——山和海，不会忘掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有海，就有波涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有涛，这声音不会衰老。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虎门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大虎山，小虎山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守着铜关铁锁的虎门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万国樯橹于此有自在的扬程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"导航灯梦一样柔润。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，“快蟹”“扒龙”靠近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它就有真正的虎性。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山，多了一百五十个年轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海，多了一百五十个年轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虎并没有睡去，它总那么清醒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：“快蟹”“扒龙”，是当年帝国主义武装走私鸦片的快艇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"销烟池"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虎门销烟池"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史火山的一个出口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排荡激越的熔浆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇成热流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映红云空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至今流星划过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是当年拂落的遗星？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}